Play League of Legends FREE at http://signup.leagueoflegends.com/?ref=VayneArt If there's anything that Vayne teaches us it's that even if you're at home in the shadows, it never hurts to look good. And while we're on the subject of looking good, Riot Games artists Katie DeSousa and Wes Keil are here to bring you a warden of the night that's as fierce as the vile creatures she hunts, yet as captivating as the midnight moon. While the heels of steel and ruby red glasses might show off her elegant sense of style, don't let that fool you. Her crossbows still let you know she means business.
